Cook bacon and chicken bacon as required. Start with 2 slices of sourdough bread. Squirt both pieces with the Sandwich Spread. Layer 2 ounces Provolone Cheese, 2 ounces Peppadew Cheese and 2 ounces Smoked Gouda Cheese onto bread. Add 4 slices either Bacon or Chicken Bacon and 2 tomato slices per sandwich. Top with second slice of bread. Can be cooked on a griddle or in a panini press. Cook just until the cheese starts to melt. Serve warm.